## Hints for Future Agents
- The skill's imperative example REQUIRES weave.init() (or some real SDK
  TracerProvider) to be active. Under the default OTel proxy/NoOp provider,
  log_turn/log_session can raise on turn_span.context instead of no-oping.
- Emitted span names are the convention to teach: invoke_agent <agent>, chat
  <model>, execute_tool <tool>. operation_name column derives from these.

## Codebase Discoveries
- weave.init() returns the WeaveClient and installs the session OTel provider as
  a side effect (only if no TracerProvider is already set, and only if a trace
  server URL is configured).

